4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge who aspire to become cybersecurity specialists. This 16-week program includes three live online classes each week, with a maximum class size of 16 participants. Students will acquire foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, along with expertise in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. Graduates receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by various institutions. The program is available in English and Spanish, catering to diverse learner needs. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop